snippet.title: DAY ONE: GARRY'S INCIDENT Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
CGRtrailers, from Classic Game Room®, presents a gameplay trailer for DAY ONE: GARRY'S INCIDENT from Wild Games Studio. Day One: Garry's Incident will be released this October 2012 on the PC via Steam. Enjoy!

Be sure to check out more video game clips, previews and trailers from Classic Game Room's CGRtrailers at http://www.youtube.com/CGRtrailers

Check out more reviews from Classic Game Room at: http://www.youtube.com/ClassicGameRoom and http://www.youtube.com/CGRundertow
